creator: Felt Cards
descriptionHtml:
HOW IT WORKS

1. Select a card design (for any occasion) or photos from your phone.

2. Handwrite your message using just your finger or a stylus. (Don’t worry you can type too, and we have several fun designer fonts to choose from.)

3. Add up to three additional photos or card designs to create a one-of-a-kind accordion-style card.

4. We then print your card on premium Mohawk paper and mail it with a hand-applied stamp, within 24 hours.


FLOWERS, CASH MONEY, GIFT CARDS, AND MORE.

We take thoughtfulness seriously and know that you do too. That’s why we constantly bring in new, interesting and novel items that you can send with your card. We always have a seasonal fresh-cut flower, bath bombs, and hang dried lavender. During holidays we add new items like pumpkins (with carving kits) for a fun Halloween surprise.

All of our gifts and cards ship together, in the same box. Some companies ship your gift and card separately.


FROM EVERY DAY, TO YOUR BIG DAY

Use Felt to send everyday cards and all occasions in between:

- Photo cards
- Birthday cards
- Thank you cards
- Greeting cards
- Wedding cards
- Anniversary cards
- Grandparents cards
- Baby cards
- Congratulatory cards
- Valentine’s Day cards
- Sympathy cards
- Graduation cards
- Gift cards
- Postcards
- Custom cards


CARD DETAILS

- Cards are 4” wide x 4.5” tall.
- Send just one in an envelope, or pick up to four and create an accordion-style card.
- Accordion style cards have a micro-perforation between each fold.
- We use premium Mohawk paper and mail in kraft envelopes.


PRICING & SHIPPING

Cards start at just $4, including postage! Add additional card frames for only $1.
Cards ship anywhere in the world for only $1 more per recipient.
Buy Felt Credits and cards start as low as $3.00 or subscribe and send 3 cards a month for only $5.

Oh snap, there’s more:
- Delayed delivery: Write a card today and select a future delivery date. No more missing a birthday ;)
- Drafts: Save drafts to finish later or completed cards to send again.
- Address Book: We save all your contacts to make it easy to send a card again.
- Birthday Reminders: Add a birthday, anniversary or any other event and we’ll remind you 10 days before so you can send a card on time.
- Custom Cards: Custom cards for your personal needs are available. You can provide us your design to print or work with us to create your own private card. Email feltpro@feltapp.com to let us know you're interested.



We love your feedback. Email us at hi@feltapp.com. We read them all.
And thank you for all of your reviews! They really do help other people discover Felt.

descriptionShort: Send personal, handwritten photo & greeting cards for birthday, thank you & more
title: Greeting, Birthday Cards

creator: Felt Cards
descriptionHtml:
Felt is the highest quality, most personal way to send real, handwritten greeting cards and photos to friends and loved ones. Your handwriting is 100% authentic, like you wrote it with pen and paper. It’s personal mail for the modern world: beautiful, fun and couldn’t be simpler.

SHARK TANK | INSTYLE | NPR | NY TIMES | SXSW | REALSIMPLE | BRIT+CO | GLAMOUR

Use Felt to make greeting cards for every occasion:
• Photo Cards
• Thank You Cards
• Birthday Cards
• Holiday Cards
• Grandparents
• Babies
• Weddings
• Graduation Cards
• Travel
• Invitations
• Father’s Day Cards
• Mother’s Day Cards
• Anniversary & Love
• Thinking of You Cards
• Get Well Soon Cards
• Congratulations

DETAILS

Felt greeting cards are mailed within 24 hrs. Monday - Friday.

Our greeting cards are 4 inches wide x 4.5 inches tall. We call them card frames. You can connect up to four frames to create one amazing greeting card!

Select from greeting card designs made by independent artists.

We use premium Mohawk paper and envelopes.- We hand apply a first class stamp.- You can send your greeting card to one person or multiple recipients at once.

Felt greeting cards start at just $4.50 (including postage) or send unlimited greeting cards for $10 a month.- Volume discounts are available in the app for larger card sending needs.

Adding contacts is easy! Import them right from your phone into the app or upload a spreadsheet here: www.my.feltapp.com

HOW IT WORKS

Select one of our many original greeting card designs, or select a photo from your phone. Then write a personal message on the front or back of the card with a stylus or your finger. (Don’t worry you can type too, and we have several fun designer fonts to choose from.) We print your cards, photos and handwritten message on premium Mohawk card stock.

Larger greeting cards with multiple panels come in our own unique accordion-style format, with micro-perforations between each fold. We seal them by hand, add a first class hand-applied stamp and mail them within 24hrs, Monday - Friday.

You can send a greeting card to just one person or send the same card or photos to lots of friends and family, to share and preserve your special memories. Felt is used by brides and new mom’s for sending all their thank you’s and it’s perfect for holiday greeting cards or any occasion.

Send Later: Write a card today and select a future date for your greeting cards to arrive by. (No more missing your BFF's birthday because you had to wait until the last minute...and then forgot.)

Templates: Save cards to finish later or send the same card again in the future without having to re-write the message.

Address Book: We save all your contacts in the Felt address book! Easily keep track of the addresses you wrote, and quickly add multiple recipients to your order.

Birthday Reminders: Add a reminder for your friend’s birthday, anniversary or any other event and we’ll remind you ten days before so you can send a birthday card on time.

Add real cash or gift cards, or a one of our curated gifts to your order for birthday cards, holiday cards, or just because.

International Shipping: Ship a Card anywhere in the world for only $1 more per recipient.

Volume Discounts: You can purchase Felt Credits and save up to 25% on every order.

Custom Greeting Cards: Custom greeting cards for your personal needs are available. You can provide us your design or work with us to create your own private card. Email hi@feltapp.com to let us know you're interested.
